sentence: list the flights from new york to miami on a tuesday which are nonstop and cost less than four hundred sixty six dollars
sq2:
SELECT DISTINCT  v0.stops, '"'||v1.airport_code||'"', '"'||v2.city_code||'"',
 '"'||v2.city_name||'"', '"'||v3.airport_code||'"',
 '"'||v4.city_code||'"', '"'||v4.city_name||'"', '"'||v5.days_code||'"',
 '"'||v5.day_name||'"', '"'||v6.flight_id||'"',
 '"'||v7.fare_id||'"', v7.round_trip_cost, '"'||v8.fare_basis_code||'"',
 '"'||v9.days_code||'"', '"'||v9.day_name||'"' FROM flight v0,
 airport_service v1, city v2, airport_service v3,
 city v4, days v5, flight_fare v6, fare v7, fare_basis v8,
 days v9 
WHERE ((v0.stops =  0) AND (((v0.from_airport = ANY v1.airport_code) 
AND ((v1.city_code = ANY v2.city_code) 
AND (v2.city_name = 'NEW YORK'))) AND (((v0.to_airport = ANY v3.airport_code) 
AND ((v3.city_code = ANY v4.city_code) 
AND (v4.city_name = 'MIAMI'))) AND (((v0.flight_days = ANY v5.days_code) 
AND (v5.day_name = 'TUESDAY')) AND ((v0.flight_id = ANY v6.flight_id) 
AND ((v6.fare_id = ANY v7.fare_id) 
AND ((v7.round_trip_cost <  466) AND ((v7.fare_basis_code = ANY v8.fare_basis_code) 
AND ((v8.basis_days = ANY v9.days_code) 
AND (v9.day_name = 'TUESDAY'))))))))));
